| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3545 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0ff1e812-67cb-56a2-828e-1f9c2bdee052"
